  "title": "Marketing Solution Lead // Performance Incentives",
  "description": "<p>🚀<strong> Looking for to upgrade &amp; take your career to the next level?</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>🌎<strong> Who We Are</strong></p>\n<p>Royal Organisation is a global leader in sales and marketing. We help brands grow through direct, in-person strategies that deliver results. At the same time, we build a high-performing team driven by growth, trust, and clear goals.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>💡<strong> What You’ll Do</strong></p>\n<p>• Develop and execute marketing and sales strategies</p>\n<p>• Build strong relationships with customers through face-to-face engagement</p>\n<p>• Analyze sales data and market trends to improve results</p>\n<p>• Lead and manage direct marketing campaigns</p>\n<p>• Set and hit clear, measurable sales targets</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>🛠<strong> What We Look For</strong></p>\n<p>• Confidence in leading sales initiatives and working with a team</p>\n<p>• Strong communication and negotiation skills</p>\n<p>• Ability to build trust and long-term customer relationships</p>\n<p>• Good with numbers and data-driven decisions</p>\n<p>• Proven ability to meet or exceed performance targets</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>🔥<strong> What You’ll Gain</strong></p>\n<p>• Travel perks, both local and international ✈️</p>\n<p>• One-on-one mentorship to help you grow fast 👨‍🏫</p>\n<p>• Real career advancement with hands-on experience 📈</p>\n<p>• A supportive, team-focused environment 😃</p>\n<p>• Weekly earnings with no income cap 💰</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>A simple decision today could lead to something bigger tomorrow.</strong></p>",
